The '''Hive Council''' was the government body of the [[X'Ting]] of [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]].

Located beneath the city of [[ChikatLik]], the Council contained twelve elder representatives, one for each of the planet's hives. A member of the Council was addressed as "my lord."

The Hive Council advised the [[Regent/Legends|Regent]]. [[Caiza Quill]] was a member.

